#Fighting Ships  of the Shattered Imperium
#    SIZE J   G  GTL
#There are 2 fleet types (except for Depot fleets, see below).
# Numbered
# Reserve
#Numbered fleets are numbered 1-999 (approximately 320 Numbered fleets).
#Reserve fleets are numbered 1001-1999.
#Depots have 3 fleet types to account for protection & convenience value
# Training
# Mothball
# Security
#Named fleets are made up of Numbered fleets
